data.title: Traverse City Eyemart Express
data.text:
Best possible vision.

Traverse Eye Care Services is the private practice of Dr. Marc Austhof where we bring value using state of the art technology at affordable rates.

Our goal is to provide every patient with the best possible vision and maintain the health of your eyes for the future.

We strive to offer exceptional eye exams for glasses, contact lenses, and all types of treatment and management of eye diseases and disorders. We are located inside Eyemart Express Traverse City.

Read more information

Traverse Eye Care Services is also a Certified Ranger Shooting glass Dealer. Check out all the latest and greatest in Shooting eyewear technology at reranger.com

We offer new brands, new styles at great prices.

We have a wide variety of selections. Our staff will assist you to find the best options and fit in frames and lenses for your eyewear needs.
